Weche mag Lemuel


1  Magi e weche matut mane min ruoth Lemuel opuonje:


2  “En ang’o, yaye wuoda? Ere gima dawachi?

In ema Nyasaye nomiyai

bang’ winjo lemo mane akuong’oranego.


3  Kik iketh tekri kuom mon,

kata kik iwit mwanduni duto kuomgi,

nikech giseketho ruodhi mang’eny.


4  Yaye, wuoda Lemuel, chik iti ni gima awacho.

Ruodhi ok onego omadh kong’o

kendo ok onego gigomb madho gik mamero ji,


5  nimar ka gimetho to wigi wil gi chik,

kendo giketho buch joma odhier machandore.


6  Joma tho, kendo joma chunygi lit ema mondo imi kong’o,


7  eka wigi owil gi chan kod chuny lit ma gin-go.


8  Kik iwe mak ichwako joma odhier ma ok nyal konyore kendgi.


9  Ee, nyaka iwuo mondo ong’adnigi bura kare.”

Dhako malong’o


10  Dhako malong’o ber moloyo kite ma nengogi tek.

Mano kaka yudo dhako ma kamano tek!


11  Chwore oketo geno mare kuome,

omiyo chworeno ok nyal bedo jachan.


12  E ngimane duto otimo ni chwore mana gik mabeyo kende.


13  Otiyo matek, koloso lewni mabeyo gi yie rombe kod tworo.


14  Kaka yiedhi a kuonde maboyo ka kelo gik moko,

e kaka dhakono bende kelo chiemo moago oko.


15  Omondo chiew mondo olos ni joode chiemo,

kendo onyis jotichne manyiri gik ma onego gitim.


16  Ka odwaro ng’iewo puodho, to orango puodhono maber,

eka ong’iewe gi pesane owuon, bang’e opidhoe mzabibu.


17  Otimo kinda, kendo otiyo tijene duto gi teko, mathoth.


18  Oneno ni gik moloso kelone ohala,

omiyo omoko taya, kendo otiyogo koda ka seche mag otieno.


19  Ochueyo yie rombo kendo olosogo law owuon.


20  Ong’won ni joma odhier, kendo okonyo joma chandore.


21  Ok odew kata ka koyo ng’ich,

nikech joode nigi lewni maliet ma girwako.


22  Ochueyo lewni mipedho e kitendni.


23  Chwore en jabura mong’ere

kendo en achiel kuom jodong piny.


24  Dhakono bende loso lewni gi misibe mondo johala ong’iew.


25  Oratego kendo ji ogene,

bende ndalo mabiro ok goye kibaji.


26  Ka owuoyo to owuoyo gi rieko,

kendo opuonjo ji gi muolo.


27  Pile odich korango gik ma joode ochando.


28  Nyithinde goyone erokamano.

Chwore bende pake, ka wacho niya,


29  “Mon mang’eny beyo, to in ema iloyogi duto.”


30  Ber mar wang’ wuondo ji.

Adier, chia bende rumo,

to dhako ma oluoro Ruoth Nyasaye ema yudo pak.


31  Miye pak moromo gi gik ma otimo,

kendo ji duto mondo omiye luor.

